title: Topology on the real projective line

Consider the [[homeomorphism|Hom√∂omorphismus]] $$S^1\to\Bbb R\mathrm P^1$$

$$
\begin{pmatrix} \cos\alpha \\ \sin\alpha\end{pmatrix}\mapsto
\begin{bmatrix} \cos 2\alpha \\ \sin 2\alpha\end{bmatrix}.
$$

We define the open sets of $$\Bbb R\mathrm P^1$$ as the sets with open preimages under this map, which defines a [[topology|Topologie]].